In this module application depends on infra instead of fusing application and infra, there is no rule that prohibits this.
The queries are on their slices, but the persistence not.

delete en user lo pone todo a anonymous y deleted = true
delete en account la borra de verdad y la pasa a la tabla de datos deleteados
los de metadata deben apuntar al uuid de user, no como fk, asi no hay que anonimizarlos
el @Version lo deberia tener solo el AR
